{
    "manually_checked": false,
    "poem_title": "Al digno y sabio intendente don Alejandro Ramírez",
    "author": "Alejandro Tapia y Rivera",
    "poem_alt_title": "Triste la hermosa Borinquen gemía",
    "corpus": "disco2_1",
    "stanzas": [
        {
            "stanza_number": "1",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "1",
                    "line_text": "Triste la hermosa Borinquen gemía",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+--+--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "2",
                    "line_text": "arrastrando la mísera pobreza,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "3",
                    "line_text": "ella que el don de perenal riqueza",
                    "metrical_pattern": "+--+---+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "4",
                    "line_text": "en sus campos feraces contenía.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Triste la hermosa Borinquen gemía\narrastrando la mísera pobreza,\nella que el don de perenal riqueza\nen sus campos feraces contenía."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "2",
            "stanza_type": "cuarteto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "5",
                    "line_text": "El cielo que amoroso la quería",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "6",
                    "line_text": "no pudo consentir en su terneza",
                    "metrical_pattern": "++---+---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "7",
                    "line_text": "que sufriese tan bárbara dureza,",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+-++---+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "8",
                    "line_text": "la que el yugo del mal no merecía.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--++--+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "El cielo que amoroso la quería\nno pudo consentir en su terneza\nque sufriese tan bárbara dureza,\nla que el yugo del mal no merecía."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "3",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "9",
                    "line_text": "De Power escuchó la alta plegaria",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+--+-+--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "10",
                    "line_text": "(del patriótico amor grato suspiro)",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "11",
                    "line_text": "y ordenó que a cambiar la era precaria",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--++--+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "De Power escuchó la alta plegaria\n(del patriótico amor grato suspiro)\ny ordenó que a cambiar la era precaria"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": "4",
            "stanza_type": "terceto",
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": "12",
                    "line_text": "en rico bienestar, fuese Ramiro...",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---++--+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "13",
                    "line_text": "Ramiro bienhechor, tu noble historia",
                    "metrical_pattern": "-+---+-+-+-"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": "14",
                    "line_text": "grabará Puerto Rico en su memoria.",
                    "metrical_pattern": "--+--+---+-"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "en rico bienestar, fuese Ramiro...\nRamiro bienhechor, tu noble historia\ngrabará Puerto Rico en su memoria."
        }
    ]
}